# Component Discovery — Search → Reuse → Extend → Create

**Firma:** HorosCode · **Produkt:** HorosCloud

**Never create a new component before searching the codebase.**

## Decision Tree

```
1. SEARCH  — Glob/Grep existing *.axaml, Styles/, Components/
2. REUSE   — Exact match exists → use as-is with bindings
3. EXTEND  — Close match → add property/style variant
4. CREATE  — No match AND 2+ repetitions in mockup → new UserControl
5. INLINE  — One-off layout element → keep in region AXAML (no over-abstract)
```

## Search Commands

```text
Glob: **/*.axaml
Grep: HorosButton, HorosCard, HorosNavItem, UserControl
Grep: BrushSurface, Spacing, Radius
```

## Reuse Example

Mockup shows a primary button → existing `HorosButton` with `Variant="Primary"`:

```xml
<components:HorosButton Variant="Primary"
                      Content="{Binding SaveLabel}"
                      Command="{Binding SaveCommand}" />
```

## Extend Example

Mockup nav item needs badge → extend `HorosNavItem`, do not fork:

```xml
<!-- HorosNavItem.axaml — add optional BadgeCount -->
<components:HorosNavItem Label="{Binding Label}"
                         Icon="{Binding Icon}"
                         BadgeCount="{Binding UnreadCount}"
                         IsActive="{Binding IsActive}" />
```

## Create Example

Mockup shows a unique KPI card repeated 4× → new UserControl:

```xml
<!-- Views/Components/HorosKpiCard.axaml -->
<UserControl x:Class="HorosCloud.Desktop.Views.Components.HorosKpiCard"
             x:DataType="vm:KpiCardViewModel">
  <Border Background="{DynamicResource BrushSurfaceDefault}"
          CornerRadius="{DynamicResource RadiusMd}"
          Padding="{DynamicResource Spacing4}">
    <StackPanel Spacing="4">
      <TextBlock Text="{Binding Label}"
                 Classes="text-muted" />
      <TextBlock Text="{Binding Value}"
                 Classes="text-heading" />
    </StackPanel>
  </Border>
</UserControl>
```

## Never

- **Never** duplicate `HorosButton` as `PrimaryButton`, `ActionButton`, …
- **Never** copy-paste identical AXAML blocks 3+ times without extracting
- **Never** import Web/React components into Avalonia
- **Never** create abstractions for single-use layout elements

